## 6. Key Design Patterns to Introduce

### `AsyncTableLoader<T>` тАФ Eliminates Copy-Paste in List Controllers
```java
public class AsyncTableLoader<T> {
    public void load(
        Callable<List<T>> dataFetcher,
        TableView<T> table,
        ProgressIndicator spinner,
        Consumer<FilteredList<T>> onLoaded,
        Consumer<Throwable> onError
    ) { /* reusable loadтЖТfilterтЖТsortтЖТbind logic */ }
}
```

### `ReportParamBuilder` тАФ Fluent Null-Safe Parameter Construction
```java
Map<String, Object> params = ReportParamBuilder.create()
    .put("ORDER_NUMBER", order.getOrderNumber())
    .putIfNotNull("DEBTOR_NAME", order.getDebtor(), Debtor::getFullName)
    .putAmount("AMOUNT", order.getAmount(), tafqeetService)
    .build();
```

### Enum Arabic Labels тАФ Replace Switch Statements
```java
public enum OrderStatus {
    DRAFT("┘Е╪│┘И╪п╪й"), ISSUED("┘Е┘П╪╡╪п╪▒"), DISPATCHED("┘Е┘П╪▒╪│┘Д"),
    CANCELLED("┘Е┘П┘Д╪║┘Й"), REDUCED("┘Е┘П╪о┘Б╪╢");

    private final String arabicLabel;
    // ...
}
```

