## 7. Performance Improvements Summary

| Issue | Current | After Fix | Multiplier |
|---|---|---|---|
| Load 100 orders | 301 queries | 1 query (JOIN) | **~300x** |
| Dashboard stats | Sync on FX thread | Async | No freeze |
| DB connection timeout | 30s hang | 5s fail-fast | **6x faster feedback** |
| Report compilation | Every time | Cached (already done тЬЕ) | тАФ |
| Local DB startup | Blocks FX thread | Background thread | No freeze |

